videos.headline: Texas' Ehlinger lofts 26-yard TD pass
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger finds Collin Johnson for a 26-yard touchdown pass to give Texas a 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Pooka Williams Jr. spins and reverses field on 11-yard run
videos.description: Kansas' Pooka Williams Jr. takes the pitch and decides to reverse field for crazy 11-yard gain.

videos.headline: Tre Williams' 31-yard run sets up Ehlinger's 5-yard TD pass
videos.description: Texas takes a 14-0 lead on a 5-yard touchdown pass from Sam Ehlinger to Andrew Beck, set up by a 31-yard scamper by Tre Williams.

videos.headline: Pooka Williams Jr. rips of 57-yard TD
videos.description: Kansas' Pooka Williams Jr. finds an opening and outruns Texas for a 57-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Kansas' Bender fires 31-yard TD pass
videos.description: Peyton Bender finds Daylon Charlot for a 31-yard touchdown to cut Texas' lead to 24-14.
